        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4491324342" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10628266377638989883">All the time, while reading it, I reminisced about <i>The Pit and the Pendulum</i> by Poe. The tales are different yet somewhere along the lines of literature, they cross a point, share a certain ambience.<br/><br/>I don’t know whether Poe and Kafka knew each other, but I’m imagining them having a cup of coffee somewhere beyond the constraints of space and time. Both are companions of dark mood and provide catharsis, at times, for us less articulate humans.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


