<div id="review_3348148284" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3348148284" />
    <a title="Janelle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/88713906-janelle"><img alt="Janelle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1581393896p2/88713906.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3348148284?book_show_action=true">May 20, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janelle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janelle" href="/user/show/88713906-janelle">Janelle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/88713906-janelle?shelf=short-stories-and-essays">short-stories-and-essays</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3348148284" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15765187934646805806">This is such a dark story, definitely Kafkaesque! In an unnamed island penal colony a traveler is given an explanation of the workings of a torture/execution machine by an officer who is a fierce believer in this form of punishment. It goes in a direction I didn’t expect. This story is referenced in Murakami’s Kafka on the shore, where the boy who calls himself Kafka says this story is his favourite and that it is more than an allegory for life but a description of life itself. Ooh, even darker!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

